title: Faerie Wars Chronicles 1-4 Audio Books Chapterized mp3/m4b
description:
These are the Audio books to the Faerie Wars Chronicles by Herbie Brennan.  The first two are read by Gerard Doyle, and the third and fourth are read by James Daniel Wilson.

T.T So many chapters!  It kinda makes my goal break down.. But I still have broken them into chapters.

I've also made each book into an .m4b (audio book format) file. These are actually smaller in size, and they work perfectly on your iPod.

I haven't listened to these at all, so if there is anything wrong with them at all comment, and I'll try and fix the problem the best I can.
